    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-09-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-09-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="188" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d188">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Egan</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-09-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 28, 1891</hi>.</date>
                            (Received September 29.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Egan states that he has not yet received a reply to his note of the
                        preceding Saturday denying charge of conspiring made against the refugees,
                        and requesting safe-conduct, and that there were no new developments.</p>
            </div>
